    "summary": "The user expresses profound despair and existential exhaustion following several years of career-related collapse, eventually suggesting that \"stopping\" is a logical exit. The assistant consistently validates the user's feelings of grief and exhaustion while explicitly rejecting the idea of self-harm and repeatedly directing the user toward professional crisis support.",
